### Source  code  

 I  have see  the  [AuthorizationMiddleware] source code  , the  code expose  the  bug.
> https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/blob/master/src/Security/Authorization/Policy/src/AuthorizationMiddleware.cs
```
