The  72 line show  the  source code develop  want  to  ensure  the  [ [AllowAnonymousAttribute] is priority than global  authorization statements] , but  it is behind  the [72 line Authenticate code].

**[Allow Anonymous skips all authorization] do  not   take effect completely.**
So I think  the [72 -77 line code ] must  be  ahead  of  [67 -70 authentication code]

